headline: L3Harris' Iver4 580: Supporting the Royal Navy's Project Wilton; Project Wilton employs L3Harris Iver AUVs for mine hunting and surveying operations.
summary: L3Harris delivered three new Iver Autonomous Underwater Vehicles for the Royal Navy's Project Wilton to support unmanned mine hunting and survey operations. The robotic boats detect and neutralize...
